Conflicts: python3-minimal, python@PYTHON_MINOR@-minimal, dhi-python3-minimal
Replaces: python3-minimal, dhi-python3-minimal
@PROVIDES_PYTHON3_MINIMAL@
Description: Minimal subset of the Python language (version @PYTHON_MINOR@)
 Interpreter binary for Python @PYTHON_MINOR@.

Package: python-@PYTHON_MINOR@
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: allowed
Depends:
