Conflicts: libpython3-dev, libpython@PYTHON_MINOR@-dev, dhi-libpython3-dev
Replaces: libpython3-dev, libpython@PYTHON_MINOR@-dev, dhi-libpython3-dev
@PROVIDES_LIBPYTHON3_DEV@
Description: Header files and development files for Python (version @PYTHON_MINOR@)
 Header files (Python.h), the unversioned shared library development symlink,
 and pkg-config files needed to build C extensions or embed Python @PYTHON_MINOR@.

Package: python-@PYTHON_MINOR@-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: allowed
Depends:
