@PROVIDES_PYTHON3_DEV@
Description: Header files and development tools for Python (version @PYTHON_MINOR@)
 Development tooling (python@PYTHON_MINOR@-config and convenience symlinks) for
 building Python @PYTHON_MINOR@ C extensions. Pulls in libpython-@PYTHON_MINOR@-dev.
